review:
I must say I really enjoy this game. Yes, it has its fair share of bugs and glitches, but its a small price to pay when you know the game is actively being worked on. The dev, MrBungle seems to really love this project he's made, and it shows;

Whenever I've had any issues with the game and posted it unto the discussions page, he was very quick to respond, sometimes in mere minutes. I have seen other people post something and its genuinely nice to see that he actively engages with the community in trying to fix any issues that may be troubling his customers.

I don't mind the bugs as I know they'll be gone in a few patches.
